@startuml
!theme plain

title MeshHook Performance Benchmarks Integration

actor Developer
boundary CI_CD "CI/CD Pipeline"
control "Benchmark\nScripts" as Benchmarks
database "Supabase\n(Postgres)" as Supabase
entity "Existing\nAPI Endpoints" as APIs
collections "MeshHook\nCodebase" as Codebase
node "Worker\nOrchestration" as Workers

Developer --> Codebase : Reviews & Identifies\nPerformance Points
Developer --> Benchmarks : Develops & Integrates
Benchmarks ..> Supabase : Measures Performance\nAgainst Database
Benchmarks ..> APIs : Measures API\nPerformance
Benchmarks ..> Workers : Measures Worker\nEfficiency
Codebase --> Supabase : Utilizes for\nData Storage & Queue Mgmt
Codebase --> APIs : Defines & Consumes
Codebase --> Workers : Utilizes for Task\nExecution & Orchestration
Supabase --> APIs : Triggers via\nRealtime Updates
Workers --> Supabase : Updates & Queries\nData
Benchmarks --> CI_CD : Integrated for\nAutomated Testing
CI_CD --> Developer : Alerts on\nRegression Detection

note right of Benchmarks : Automates Performance\nBenchmarking & Analysis

@enduml